Exam 1: Bayes discriminiant

X1 = matrix(c(2, 4, 3, 3, 12, 10, 8, 10), nrow=4)
X2 = matrix(c(5, 3, 4, 7, 9, 5), nrow=3)
X0 = c(2,8)
q  = c(0.4,0.6)
mu1 = colMeans(X1) 
mu2 = colMeans(X2) 
n1 = dim(X1)[1]
n2 = dim(X2)[1]
p  = dim(X1)[2]
V1 = (n1-1)*cov(X1)
V2 = (n2-1)*cov(X2)
S  = (V1+V2)/(n1+n2-2)
#### 计算广义平方距离
d1 = mahalanobis(X0, mu1, S)-2*log(q[1])
d2 = mahalanobis(X0, mu2, S)-2*log(q[2])
d1
## [1] 6.832581
d2
## [1] 6.438318
#### 计算后验概率
p1 = exp(-0.5*d1)/(exp(-0.5*d1)+exp(-0.5*d2))
p2 = exp(-0.5*d2)/(exp(-0.5*d1)+exp(-0.5*d2))
p1
## [1] 0.450876
p2
## [1] 0.549124

Exam 2: 利用模拟数据绘制Bayes方法、LDA方法和QDA方法的决策边界，并计算错误率

编写下面的函数classify()

library(mvtnorm)
library(MASS)
library(latex2exp)

classify = function(formula, data, mu1, mu2, sig1, sig2){
  yname = as.character(formula[[2]])
  x1name = as.character(formula[[3]][[2]])
  x2name = as.character(formula[[3]][[3]])
  n1 = sum((data[,3]=='A'))
  n2 = sum((data[,3]=='B'))
  
  obj.lda = lda(formula, data=data, prior=c(1,1)/2)
  plda = predict(object=obj.lda, newdata=data)
  error.lda = table(data[,yname] == plda$class)[[1]]/nrow(data)
  
  obj.qda = qda(formula, data=data)
  pqda = predict(object=obj.qda, newdata=data)
  error.qda = table(data[,yname] == pqda$class)[[1]]/nrow(data)
  
  q1 = n1/(n1+n2)
  q2 = n2/(n1+n2)
  p1.bayes = dmvnorm(data[,1:2], mu1, sig1)
  p2.bayes = dmvnorm(data[,1:2], mu2, sig2)
  pos = q1*p1.bayes/(q1*p1.bayes+q2*p2.bayes)
  pbayes = matrix(nrow = n1+n2, ncol = 1)
  for (i in 1:(n1+n2)){
    if (pos[i]>0.5){
      pbayes[i,1] = as.character('A')
    }else{
      pbayes[i,1] = as.character('B')
    }
  }
  pbayes = as.factor(pbayes)
  error.bayes = (table(data[,3] == pbayes)[[1]])/nrow(data)
  
  plot(data[,c(x1name,x2name)],pch=ifelse(data[,yname]==data[1,yname],18,20),col=ifelse(data[,yname]==data[1,yname],2,4),xlab = TeX('$X_1$'),ylab = TeX('$X_2$'))
  gmean = obj.lda$prior %*% obj.lda$means
  const = as.numeric(gmean %*% obj.lda$scaling)
  slope = - obj.lda$scaling[1] / obj.lda$scaling[2]
  intercept = const / obj.lda$scaling[2]
  abline(intercept, slope,lty = 2,col = 'black',lwd = 2)
  
  x1 = seq(floor(min(data[,x1name])/10)*10,ceiling(max(data[,x1name])/10)*10,length.out=2000)
  x2 = seq(floor(min(data[,x2name])/10)*10,ceiling(max(data[,x2name])/10)*10,length.out=2000)
  z = as.matrix(expand.grid(x1,x2), 0)
  colnames(z) = c(x1name, x2name)
  z = as.data.frame(z)
  m = length(x1)
  n = length(x2)
  z.qda = as.numeric(predict(object=obj.qda,newdata=z)$class)
  contour(x1,x2,matrix(z.qda,m,n),1,add=TRUE, drawlabels =FALSE, lty = 4,lwd = 2,col = 'blue')
  p1 = dmvnorm(z,mu1,sig1)
  p2 = dmvnorm(z,mu2,sig2)
  z.bayes = (q1*p1)/(q1*p1+q2*p2)
  contour(x1,x2,matrix(z.bayes,m,n),1,0.5,add=TRUE, drawlabels =FALSE, lty = 1,lwd = 2,col = 'purple')
  legend("topleft",legend=c('LDA','QDA','Bayes'),lty = c(2,4,1),col=c('black','blue','purple'),x.intersp = 0.5,y.intersp = 0.8)
  
  print(paste("Classification error rate of LDA:",error.lda))
  print(paste("Classification error rate of QDA:",error.qda))
  print(paste("Classification error rate of Bayes:",error.bayes))
}

第一种情形：两正态总体协方差矩阵相等

set.seed(100)
sig = matrix(c(1,0.3,0.3,1), 2, 2)
n1 = 180
mu1 = c(-1, 1)
n2 = 200
mu2 = c(1.5, 2)

d1 = data.frame(mvrnorm(n1,mu1,sig),as.factor(rep('A',n1)))
d2 = data.frame(mvrnorm(n2,mu2,sig),as.factor(rep('B',n2)))
colnames(d1) = c('x1','x2', 'classification')
colnames(d2) = c('x1','x2', 'classification')
data = rbind(d1, d2)

classify(classification~x1+x2, data, mu1, mu2, sig, sig)

XA = salmon[1:50,2:3]        #### Alaskan
XC = salmon[51:100,2:3]      #### Canadian

XA.mean = colMeans(XA)       #### Alaskan三文鱼数据的均值
XC.mean = colMeans(XC)       #### Canadian三文鱼数据的均值

S.pooled = 49*(cov(XA)+cov(XC))/98                #### the pooled estimator of Sigma
w  = solve(S.pooled)%*%(XA.mean-XC.mean)
w0 = -(XA.mean+XC.mean)%*%w/2
lines(salmon[,2],-(w[1,1]*salmon[,2]+w0)/w[2,1])  #### 线性判别函数的决策线

附录：discriminiant.distance函数和distinguish.distance函数

引自薛毅，陈立萍 (2007). 统计建模与R语言. 北京: 清华大学出版.

discriminiant.distance=function
   (TrnX1, TrnX2, TstX = NULL, var.equal = FALSE){
   if (is.null(TstX) == TRUE) TstX=rbind(TrnX1,TrnX2)
   if (is.vector(TstX) == TRUE)  TstX=t(as.matrix(TstX))
   else if (is.matrix(TstX) != TRUE)
      TstX=as.matrix(TstX)
   if (is.matrix(TrnX1) != TRUE) TrnX1=as.matrix(TrnX1)
   if (is.matrix(TrnX2) != TRUE) TrnX2=as.matrix(TrnX2)

   nx=nrow(TstX)
   blong=matrix(rep(0, nx), nrow=1, byrow=TRUE, 
         dimnames=list("blong", 1:nx))
   mu1=colMeans(TrnX1); mu2=colMeans(TrnX2) 
   if (var.equal == TRUE  || var.equal == T){
      S=var(rbind(TrnX1,TrnX2))
      w=mahalanobis(TstX, mu2, S)-mahalanobis(TstX, mu1, S)
   }
   else{
      S1=var(TrnX1); S2=var(TrnX2)
      w=mahalanobis(TstX, mu2, S2)-mahalanobis(TstX, mu1, S1)
   }
   for (i in 1:nx){
      if (w[i]>0)
          blong[i]="A"
      else
          blong[i]="B"
   }
   blong
}
distinguish.distance=function
   (TrnX, TrnG, TstX = NULL, var.equal = FALSE){
   if ( is.factor(TrnG) == FALSE){
       mx=nrow(TrnX); mg=nrow(TrnG)
       TrnX=rbind(TrnX, TrnG)
       TrnG=factor(rep(1:2, c(mx, mg)))
   }
   if (is.null(TstX) == TRUE) TstX=TrnX
   if (is.vector(TstX) == TRUE)  TstX=t(as.matrix(TstX))
   else if (is.matrix(TstX) != TRUE)
      TstX=as.matrix(TstX)
   if (is.matrix(TrnX) != TRUE) TrnX=as.matrix(TrnX)

   nx=nrow(TstX)
   blong=matrix(rep(0, nx), nrow=1, dimnames=list("blong", 1:nx))
   g=length(levels(TrnG))
   mu=matrix(0, nrow=g, ncol=ncol(TrnX))
   for (i in 1:g)
      mu[i,]=colMeans(TrnX[TrnG==i,]) 
   D=matrix(0, nrow=g, ncol=nx)
   if (var.equal == TRUE  || var.equal == T){
      for (i in 1:g)
         D[i,]= mahalanobis(TstX, mu[i,], var(TrnX))
   }
   else{
      for (i in 1:g)
         D[i,]= mahalanobis(TstX, mu[i,], var(TrnX[TrnG==i,]))
   }
   for (j in 1:nx){
      dmin=Inf
      for (i in 1:g)
          if (D[i,j]<dmin){
             dmin=D[i,j]; blong[j]=i
      }
   }
   blong
}
